IIUC this is unconditionally activating all the worker request bundles, whereas in the loop below we still check num_bytes_available_. Is this intended?

It seems like it would be more robust to me to do something like this instead:
```
while any(inactive worker request bundles):
   while not space remaining and any(active task bundles):
      deactivate task bundle
   if space remaining:
      activate worker request bundle
   else:
      break

while space remaining and any(inactive task bundle):
   activate task bundle

while over capacity:
   deactivate task bundle

while over capacity:
  deactivate worker request bundle
```

